It also involves deep learning techniques for multi-task learning, which is a common approach in the field of NLP. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper involves the use of neural networks for prediction tasks. Additionally, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CY (Computers and Society) could also be possible sub-categories, as the paper deals with fact-checking and political debates, which are relevant to these fields.
